Synergy 2 Specification README
==============================

Build document
--------------

build.py -pl synergy2-spec\synergy2-spec.tex

Requirements
------------

All:
  pgf-umlsd 0.2 (http://code.google.com/p/pgf-umlsd/)

Windows:
  MiKTeX (miktex.org)
  Install package: pgf-umlsd
  - See troubleshooting section to downgrade to 0.2

Ubuntu:
  Run: sudo apt-get install texlive texlive-metapost
  Download pgf-umlsd-0.2.tar.gz
    - Extract to: /usr/share/texmf-texlive/tex/late/pgf-umlsd
    - Run: mktexlsr

Reccomended viewer
------------------

Windows: Sumatra PDF
  http://blog.kowalczyk.info/software/sumatrapdf/

Troubleshooting
---------------

Error:
  ! LaTeX Error: Environment sdloop undefined.

Solution:
  Downgrade pgf-umlsd to version 0.2:
    http://code.google.com/p/pgf-umlsd/downloads/detail?name=pgf-umlsd-0.2.tar.gz

  Install to directory:
    tex\latex\pgf-umlsd
